data.body:
- VSCode Version: 1.3.1
- OS Version: Windows 10 Enterprise

Steps to Reproduce:

1.When my extension has following code, while the `previewUri` is fixed for each time, the title of preview pane is always the value of the first time.

``` typescript
commands.executeCommand('vscode.previewHtml', previewUri, ViewColumn.Two, `${Date.now()}`).then((success) => {
                }, (reason) => {
                    window.showErrorMessage(reason);
                });
```
